; HeroNicola is HIDDEN here — the player IS Nicola in the Empress
; scenarios, so showing the figure inside the same boat would be
; Nicola watching herself. (For the Emperor scenarios, replace
; with HeroDante; for Paul-at-Table-17 scenarios, with the Paul
; model when available.)
[node name="HeroNicola" parent="." instance=ExtResource("4_nicola")]
